author: Mark Twain
message: There are basically two types of people. People who accomplish things, and people who claim to have accomplished things. The first group is less crowded.
title: Thought of the day

author: Winifred Holtby
message: The things that one most wants to do are the things that are probably most worth doing.
title: Thought of the day

author: Abraham Lincoln
message: Always bear in mind that your own resolution to succeed is more important than any one thing.
title: Thought of the day

author: Albert Einstein
message: Setting an example is not the main means of influencing another, it is the only means.
title: Thought of the day
